  <chapter id="models">
    <title>Models</title>

    <section id="models_cognitive_model">
      <title>Cognitive Models</title>

      <para>Cognitive models represent users of interactive systems.</para>

      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
          <para>Hierarchical models represent a user's task and goal
          structure.</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Linguistic models represent the user-system grammar.</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Physical and device models represent human motor
          skills.</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Cognitive architectures underlie all of these cognitive
          models.</para>
        </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>

